# VenCap — Environment Variables
#
# FRED API Key (Free)
# Get yours at: https://fred.stlouisfed.org/docs/api/api_key.html
# 1. Create a free account at https://fredaccount.stlouisfed.org/login/secure/
# 2. Request an API key at https://fredaccount.stlouisfed.org/apikeys
# 3. Copy the key below
#
# This enables real-time economic data in the game (interest rates, S&P 500,
# GDP, unemployment, inflation). Without it, the game uses historical data.
VITE_FRED_API_KEY=your_fred_api_key_here
